invalid type: string "Check Latest Price\nMonopoly Empire Gold Vs Silver\nThere are several versions of Monopoly Empire – some are Gold and some are\nSilver. The different versions have different brands and different tokens. The Silver\nversion also has two Super Empire cards – ‘Hands Off’ and ‘You’re Fired’.\nMonopoly Empire Versions:\nMonopoly Empire (2013) – Gold Tokens\nS CA\nn